cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use DEQN-JAX in academic work, please cite it (and the upstream Deep Equilibrium Nets method it reimplements)."
title: "DEQN-JAX"
abstract: "A global solver for recursive economic equilibria in JAX: trains a neural-network policy to satisfy a model's Euler/FOC/market-clearing conditions on the ergodic set."
version: "0.2.0"
type: software
license: MIT
authors:
