    given-names: Anna
    email: anna.smirnova@unil.ch
# URLs below are org-move-gated: a GitHub org move is pending; update on cutover.
repository-code: "https://github.com/mechanicpanic/deqn-jax"
url: "https://mechanicpanic.github.io/deqn-jax/"
keywords:
  - deep equilibrium nets
  - global solution methods
  - recursive equilibrium
  - dynamic stochastic general equilibrium
  - computational economics
  - JAX
  - neural networks
# Upstream method credit. DEQN-JAX is a JAX/Equinox reimplementation and
# extension of Deep Equilibrium Nets, developed by Simon Scheidegger and
# collaborators. All credit for the original method belongs to these authors.
